I '''Linda D. Addison''' metung yang Americanung [[poet]] (watas) ampong [[writer]] (talasulat) ning [[Horror fiction|makatukut]], [[fantasia]], ampong[[science fiction]].  I Addison iya ing mumunang  African-Americanung menyambut keng [[Bram Stoker Award]], nung nu sinambut yang makatadua kareng kayang kawatasan a tangka ''Consumed, Reduced to Beautiful Grey Ashes'' (2001)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.horror.org/stokerwinnom.htm#2001 |title=2001 Bram Stoker Award Winners |accessdate=2008-07-15 |date= }}</ref> and ''Being Full of Light, Insubstantial'' (2007)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.horror.org/stokerwinnom.htm#2007 |title=2007 Bram Stoker Award Winners |accessdate=2008-07-15 |date= }}</ref>.  She is a founding member of the CITH (Circles in the Hair) writing group<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lindaaddisonpoet.com |title=Linda Addison-Poet/Writer |accessdate=2008-07-15 |date= }}</ref>.


